<sent type="title" lang="chi" page="01a" n="1">詩經諺解 卷之十七</sent>
<sent type="title3" lang="chi" page="01a" n="2">生民之什</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01a" n="3">厥初生民이 時維姜嫄이시니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01a" n="3">그 처엄 民을 生홈이 이 姜嫄이시니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01a" n="4">生民如何오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01a" n="4">民을 生홈을 엇디뇨</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01a-01b" n="5">克禋克祀샤 以弗無子시고</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01a-01b" n="5">히 禋며 히 祀샤  子 업을 弗시고</sent><!--^히-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01b" n="1">履帝武敏샤 歆攸介攸止샤</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01b" n="1">帝의 武敏을 履샤 介 바와 止 바애 歆샤</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01b" n="2">載震載夙샤 載生載育시니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01b" n="2">곧 震며 곧 夙샤 곧 生야 곧 育시니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01b" n="3">時維后稷이시니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01b" n="3">이 后稷이시니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01b-02a" n="4">誕彌厥月야 先生如達시니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01b-02a" n="4">그 月을 彌야 몬져 生호 達티 시니</sent><!--티 ^ -->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02a" n="1">不坼不副시며 無菑無害샤</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02a" n="1">坼디 아니시며 副디 아니시며 菑 업시며 害 업샤</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02a" n="2">以赫厥靈시니 上帝不寧가</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02a" n="2"> 그 靈을 赫시니 上帝ᅵ 寧티 아니시랴</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02a" n="3">不康禋祀아 居然生子ᅵ샷다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02a" n="3">禋祀를 康티 아니신야 居然히 子를 生샷다</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02b" n="1">誕寘之隘巷대 牛羊腓字之며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02b" n="1">隘 巷애 寘대 牛羊이 腓야 字며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02b" n="2">誕寘之平林대 會伐平林며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02b" n="2">平林에 寘대 平林 伐리를 會며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02b" n="3">誕寘之寒氷대 鳥覆翼之로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02b" n="3">寒冰에 寘대 鳥ᅵ 覆며 翼놋다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02b" n="4">鳥乃去矣어 后稷呱矣시니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02b" n="4">鳥ᅵ 去야늘 后稷이 呱시니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="02b" n="5">實覃實訏샤 厥聲載路ᅵ러시니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="02b" n="5">실로 覃며 실로 訏샤 그 聲이 路애 載더시니라</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03a" n="1">誕實匍匐샤 克岐克嶷이러시니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03a" n="1">실로 匍匐샤 히 岐시며 히 嶷더시니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03a" n="2">以就口食샤 蓺之荏菽시니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03a" n="2"> 口食에 就샤 荏菽을 蓺시니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03a" n="3">荏菽旆旆며 禾役穟穟며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03a" n="3">荏菽이 旆旆며 禾의 役이 穟檖며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03a" n="4">麻麥幪幪며 瓜瓞唪唪더니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03a" n="4">麻麥이 幪幪며 瓜瓞이 唪唪더니라</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03b" n="1">誕后稷之穡이 有相之道ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03b" n="1">后稷의 穡이 相 道ᅵ 잇도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03b" n="2">茀厥豊草고 種之黃茂니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03b" n="2">그 豊草를 茀고 黃戊를 種니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03b" n="3">實方實苞며 實種實褎며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03b" n="3">실로 方며 실로 苞며 실로 種며 실로 褎며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03b" n="4">實發實秀며 實堅實好며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03b" n="4">실로 發며 실로 秀며 실로 堅며 실로 好며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="03b" n="5">實潁實栗더니 卽有邰家室시니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="03b" n="5">실로 潁며 실로 栗더니 邰예 卽야 家室을 시니라</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04a" n="1">誕降嘉種니 維秬維秠며 維穈維芑로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04a" n="1">嘉 種을 降니 秬와 秠며 穈과 芑로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04a" n="2">恒之秬秠니 是穫是畝며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04a" n="2">秬와 秠를 恒니 이예 穫야 이예 畝애 며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04a" n="3">恒之穈芑니 是任是負야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04a" n="3">穈과 芑를 恒니 이예 任며 이예 負야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04a" n="4">以歸肇祀시니라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04a" n="4"> 歸야 비로소 祠시니라</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04b" n="1">誕我祀如何오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04b" n="1">우리 祠ᅵ 엇디뇨</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04b" n="2">或舂或揄며 或簸或蹂며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04b" n="2">或 舂며 或 揄며 或 簸며 或 蹂며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04b" n="3">釋之叟叟며 烝之浮浮며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04b" n="3">釋홈을 叟叟히 며 烝홈을 浮浮히 며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04b" n="4">載謀載惟며 取蕭祭脂며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04b" n="4">곧 謀며 곧 惟며 蕭를 取야 脂로 祭며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04b" n="5">取羝以軷며 載燔載烈야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04b" n="5">羝를 取야  軷며 곧 燔며 곧 烈야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="04b-05a" n="6">以興嗣歲로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="04b-05a" n="6"> 歲를 興며 嗣도다</sent><!--^며-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05a" n="1">卬盛于豆니 于豆于登이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="1">내 豆에 盛니 豆에 며 登에 놋다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05a" n="2">其香始升니 上帝居歆이샷다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="2">그 香이 비로소 升니 上帝ᅵ 居야 歆샷다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05a" n="3">胡臭亶時리오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a" n="3">엇디 臭 진실로 時 이리오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05a-05b" n="4">后稷肇祀시므로 庶無罪悔야</sent><!--‘시므로’의 ‘므로’는 영인본에는 ‘느로’로 나타났으나 오탈자로 판단하여 수정함-->
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05a-05b" n="4">后稷이 비로소 祀심으로 거의 罪와 悔 업서</sent><!--로 ^ 거-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05b" n="1">以迄于今이샷다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="1"> 今에 迄샷다</sent>
<sent type="title4" lang="chi" page="05b" n="2">生民 八章</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05b" n="3">敦彼行葦 牛羊勿踐履면</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="3">敦 뎌 行앳 葦를 牛羊이 踐履티 말면</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05b" n="4">方苞方體야 維葉泥泥리라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="4">뵈야호로 苞며 뵈야호로 體야 葉이 泥泥리라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05b" n="5">戚戚兄弟 莫遠具爾면</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b" n="5">戚戚 兄弟를 멀이 마라 다 갓가이면</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="05b-06a" n="6">或肆之筵이며 或授之几리라</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="05b-06a" n="6">或 筵을 肆며 或 几를 授리라</sent><!--筵^을-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06a" n="1">肆筵設席니 授几有緝御ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="1">筵을 肆면 席을 設니 几를 授고 緝야 御리 잇도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06a" n="2">或獻或酢며 洗爵奠斝며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a" n="2">或 獻며 或 酢며 爵을 洗며 斝를 奠며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06a-06b" n="3">醓醢以薦며 或燔或炙며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06a-06b" n="3">醓과 醢로  薦며 或 燔며 或 炙며</sent><!--燔^-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06b" n="1">嘉殽脾臄이며 或歌或咢이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06b" n="1">嘉 殽ᅵ 脾와 臄이며 或 歌며 或 咢놋다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06b" n="2">敦弓旣堅며 四鍭旣鈞이어</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06b" n="2">敦弓이 이믜 堅며 四餱ᅵ 이믜 鈞거를</sent><!--'거를'은 ‘거늘’의 오자로 판단되나 영인본에 나타난 대로 입력함-->
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06b" n="3">舍矢旣均니 序賓以賢이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06b" n="3">矢를 舍홈애 이믜 均니 賓을 序호 賢으로  놋다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="06b-07a" n="4">敦弓旣句며 旣挾四鍭야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="06b-07a" n="4">敦弓이 이믜 句며 이믜 四餱 狹야</sent><!--弓^이-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07a" n="1">四鍭如樹니 序賓以不侮ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07a" n="1">四餱ᅵ 樹 니 賓을 序호 侮티 아니홈으로  놋다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07a" n="2">曾孫維主니 酒醴維醹ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07a" n="2">曾孫이 主니 酒醴 醹도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07a" n="3">酌以大斗야 以祈黃耈놋다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07a" n="3">酌호 大斗로  야  黃耈 祈놋다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07a-07b" n="4">黃耈台背ᅵ 以引以翼야</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07a-07b" n="4">黃耈와 台背  引며  翼야</sent><!--^며-->

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07b" n="1">壽考維祺야 以介景福이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07b" n="1">壽考로 祺야  큰 福을 介케 놋다</sent>
<sent type="title4" lang="chi" page="07b" n="2">行葦 四章</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07b" n="3">旣醉以酒ᅵ오 旣飽以德호니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07b" n="3">이믜 醉호 酒로  고 이믜 飽호 德으로  호니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="07b" n="4">君子萬年애 介爾景福이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="07b" n="4">君子ᅵ 萬年애 네 큰 福을 介케 리로다</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08a" n="1">旣醉以酒ᅵ오 爾殽旣將니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08a" n="1">이믜 醉호 酒로  고 네 殽를 이믜 將니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08a" n="2">君子萬年애 介爾昭明이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08a" n="2">君子ᅵ 萬年애 네 昭明을 介케 리로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08a" n="3">昭明有融니 高朗令終이로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08a" n="3">昭明홈이 融니 高朗야 終을 令히 리로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08a" n="4">令終有俶니 公尸嘉告ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08a" n="4">終을 令홈이 俶이 이시니 公尸ᅵ 嘉로 告놋다</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08b" n="1">其告維何오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08b" n="1">그 告홈은 엇뎨오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08b" n="2">邊豆靜嘉ᅵ어</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08b" n="2">籩豆ᅵ 靜고 嘉거</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08b" n="3">朋友攸攝이 攝以威儀로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08b" n="3">朋友의 攝 배 攝 威儀로  놋다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08b" n="4">威儀孔時어 君子有孝子ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08b" n="4">威儀 심히 時거 君子ᅵ 孝子를 둣도다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="08b" n="5">孝子不匱니 永錫爾類ᅵ로다</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="08b" n="5">孝子ᅵ 匱티 아니니 기리 네게 類를 錫리로다</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="09a" n="1">其類維何오</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="09a" n="1">그 類 엇뎨오</sent>
